</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="545">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Born the youngest of four sons to Henry and Jane Lewis Jones a Quaker family in Upper Dublin, Montgomery County, Pennsylvania. Henry Jones worked on his family's farm throughout his life.  Henry's brothers were John L, Lewis, and Clement.  Henry was married in 1850 to Mary Y. Shoemaker.  They had no children.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
